name: KeyFind (#LowRezJam 2019)
description:
NOTE: Added the HTLM5 version for accessibility. It's technically identical to the Windows version, but I can't debug it because I don't actually own Game Maker Studio 2's HTML5 module. ><;;

______

Once again, this project was made as a release to my frustrations of feeling useless with my projects over the summer.

- Guide the key to the keyhole to unlock the next level.

- Currently 24 randomized levels to play through.
